on.  "/><LineBreak/><Run Text="3.2 User Creations: You will retain the corresponding intellectual property rights to characters, buildings, or other creations you create in the game, and grant us a reasonable license to use them for the purposes of game services.  "/><LineBreak/><Run/><LineBreak/><Run Text="4. Other Terms  "/><LineBreak/><Run Text="4.1 Term Revisions: We reserve the right to modify these terms and conditions at any time and will notify users through appropriate channels.  "/><LineBreak/><Run Text="4.2 Service Termination: We reserve the right to immediately terminate or restrict your game service if you violate these terms and conditions, without further notice.  "/><LineBreak/><Run/><LineBreak/><Run Text="5. Agreement to Terms  "/><LineBreak/><Run Text="Your registration or login to the game account signifies that you have read, understood, and agreed to comply with these terms and conditions, as well as our privacy policy.  "/><LineBreak/><Run/><LineBreak/><Run Text="Thank you for choosing our game, and we wish you a pleasant gaming experience!"/></TextBlock>
